cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the selection of features for instantaneously predicting the continuous dimensions of emotional states using convolutional neural networks. This involves statistical learning and mutual information-based selection process. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
